These are Puzzles for 2x4 Level 2

.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-1::.
Beverage: cola, juice, lemonade, water
Pet: mouse, pony, cat, lizard
1. Beverage:cola is on the right of Pet:cat##1
2. Pet:lizard is on the far left##1
3. Pet:cat is between Pet:pony and Beverage:juice##2
4. Beverage:water is on the far left##1
5. Beverage:lemonade is between Beverage:juice and Beverage:cola##2

.:: Answer ::.
|            |       1       |    2    |    3     |     4      |
| Beverage   | water         | juice   | lemonade | cola       |
| Pet      | lizard | mouse | cat   | pony |

 #################################
 
.:: Puzzle 2x4-Level-2-2::.
Hobby: gardening, magic-tricks, reading, video-games
House: art-deco, farmhouse, ranch-style, tower
1. House:tower is between Hobby:reading and House:farmhouse##2
2. Hobby:video-games is on the far right##1
3. House:ranch-style is on the right of House:art-deco##1
4. Hobby:gardening is on the left of House:art-deco##1

.:: Answer ::.
|               |      1       |     2     |    3    |      4      |
| Hobby         | magic-tricks | gardening | reading | video-games |
| House   | farmhouse    | tower   | art-deco | ranch-style       |

